page.title: 05My Day by Paul Harries (11)
page.content: My name is{Paul Harries.}I am eleven years old.I was born on the 24th of December 1973.I have three{hobbies. They are{Judo,model making-lorries and {cars- and stamp-collecting. I normally get up at 6:15.The first thing after having a wash and brushing my hair and getting dressed,I ask my mum what's for breakfast.When I've laid the table I boil the kettle and tidy up.After breakfast,I help my brother to wash up.When it's time to go to school we get in car.We start school at 9:00 and finish at 3:10. After school we do our homework that mum makes us do.When I go out to play I play Football,but if it's Monday I go to Judo at 7:00.When it's bed time I go.My bedtime is 9:00.
